        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>opus sectile (technique) [300404030], inlay (process) [300053850], surface covering processes and techniques [300229469], additive and joining processes and techniques [300229467], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
